## DatePositionParser interface

Parser used for parsing date using provided format and returning positions and selected date part

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface DatePositionParser 
```

## Methods

|  Method | Description |
|  --- | --- |
|  [next(date, cursorPosition)](./datetime.datepositionparser.next.md) | Parse date as string and returns information about position and selected part of date, while moving it to next part, if it was last part returns null |
|  [parse(date, cursorPosition)](./datetime.datepositionparser.parse.md) | Parse date as string and returns information about positions and selected part of date |
|  [previous(date, cursorPosition)](./datetime.datepositionparser.previous.md) | Parse date as string and returns information about position and selected part of date, while moving it to previous part, if it was first part returns null |
